About Us
					

						North Glass Technology (Group) Co., Ltd is a comprehensive hi-tech enterprise which specializes in research & development of glass processing technology; manufacturing of the glass processing equipments and processed glass. We have 23 Chinese and international patents of the glass process equipments. The group owns the following subsidiaries: Luoyang North Glass Technology Co., Ltd, Luoyang North Glass Safety Glass Co., Ltd; Beijing North Glass Safety Glass Manufacturing Co., Ltd; Shanghai North Glass Technology Industrial Co., Ltd. The two safety glass manufacturing companies in Beijing and Luoyang have become the pre-research and training centers, which guarantees the new technology and process to enter the market with maturity.  North Glass Group has more than 1500 employees in the 4 companies that locate in 3 cities, one research institute (consists of 4 design centers) and over 180 R&D staff. North Glass Group has formed a system of self R&D, self testing, self design and self manufacturing.
					

