Company Description                    




                        Luoyang North Glass Technology Co., Ltd., founded byGao Xueming on May 18, 1995 in Luoyang High-tech Development Zone, is mainly engaged in the research, design and manufacture of glass deep-processing technologies and equipment. The company owns a registered capital of RMB 200 million and a net asset of RMB 500 million.
It is capable of producing large size arc-shaped tempered glass, Low-E coated glass production equipment, and solar control coated glass and Low-E coated glass. North Glass has three holding subsidiaries and a wholly-owned subsidiary in Luoyang, Beijing and Shanghai.                    


