Introduction



					 	 Northglass Technology (Group) Limited is a special comprehensive new- and high-tech enterprise engaged in the research and development of new glass deep processing technology, process and equipment as well as deep processed glass products. 

Northglass is the first company in China to develop horizontal roller-hearth glass tempering furnace. Northglass takes the lead in introducing to the world glass tempering furnace and tempered glass products of the largest specifications. Northglass guides the industry to the perfect realm of glass tempering, the ultimate product of super flat tempered glass without any stains. Northglass explained the true essence of the processing of Low-E glass, the new-generation technology and products of completely forced convection in the world.

Listen attentively, concern closely, promise earnestly and contribute greatly. 
Northglass will provide ideal products and perfect service to the broad customers with great sincerity and tremendous strength.
					

